    },
    {
      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "Friction belongs at the risky edge",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Rate limiting is not just reliability. It is how you make abusive loops cost more than they are worth.</p>"
        },
